project.json: this file emcompasses your nx plugin and the package name necessary to run your app.
**`project.json`** is a **configuration file that defines a single Nx project**, including its **build, test, lint tasks, executors, and settings**.

👉 In short: **it tells Nx how a project works and how to run it**.
###minimum configuration##
{
  "name": "my-project",
  "projectType": "library",
  "targets": {}
}

